### (Quick Sort)

**:** : O(N___log___N)  : O(N)  : O(N^2)
**:** O(logN) (O(logN)O(1))

* :  

```java
public void quickSort(int[] nums, int left, int right) {
    int i = left, j = right, key = nums[right];
    while(i < j) {
        while(i < j && nums[i] < key)
            i++;

        nums[j] = nums[i];

        while(i < j && nums[j] >= key)
            j--;

        nums[i] = nums[j];
    }
    nums[i] = key;

    if(i - 1 > left)
        quickSort(nums, left, i - 1);

    if(i + 1 < right)
        quickSort(nums, i + 1, right);
}
```

